    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Information that is formatted and presented in a form that is easily legible and understood by users, often allowing expressions of uncertainty and nuance. Display information is often used in conjunction with "indexing information."</Note_Text>
